Checkpoint 4: Final Validation, Results, and Recommendations

The week of April 19th - 26th was used to work on and complete Checkpoint 4 - Final Validation, Results, and Recommendations. Based on the required deliverables, the product was a fully completed system with validated performance, documented results, and final risk analysis. A quick summary of each section is given below.

1. Final System Overview
-     Describes the completed phishing detection system, including its pipeline stages (input, feature extraction, scoring, explainability, and output) and implemented security controls.
